      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>Standard organizers don't fit around the drain pipe<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Most under-sink racks either block the P-trap or leave 40% of the cabinet unused</span></td>
        <td>U-shaped shelf + adjustable legs clears P-traps and disposals<br><span style="font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted-foreground);">Slides from 15" to 25" wide and adjusts in four height steps to fit around your exact plumbing</span></td>
