<!-- §9 What is it? -->
<h2>What Exactly Is an Adjustable Under-Sink Organizer?</h2>
<p>It's a two-tier expandable steel rack engineered specifically for the under-sink environment — pipes, disposals, and all. The frame slides from 15" to 25" wide to fit most cabinets, and four shelf height positions let you dial in the exact clearance you need above your plumbing. A pull-out bottom drawer handles the small stuff (rubber gloves, drain plugs, sponges) that otherwise migrates to the back of the cabinet never to be seen again. The rust-resistant coating means cleaning product splashes won't wreck it over time.</p>

